The '''Bandercamp Auctions''' was an annual series of auctions held on [[Hinder Island]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Recopia]]. For five [[Standard week/Legends|weeks]], [[Merchant/Legends|merchants]] from all over [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] flocked to the [[Hinder Market]] to buy and sell rare creatures to dealers from the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]] and the [[Colonies/Legends|Colonies]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

To those who knew where to look, some less than scrupulous traders could be found dealing in [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]]- or near-sentient creatures at the auctions.<ref name="CCW" />

